metadata.name: Gaelia Mounts and Pets #1
metadata.description: Embark on a magical adventure with our exclusive collection of Mounts and Pets. Choose from a variety of fantastical creatures, each with its own unique appearance and abilities. Whether you're seeking a fierce dragon to serve as your trusty steed or a cute and cuddly companion to join you on your quests. Whether you're an avid collector or a seasoned player, these Mounts and Pets are sure to enhance your gaming experience and become a valued addition to your journey.
